project: Close the menu and resume the game

Spike is a local 2 versus 2 hot-seat sports game.

The two teams - green and purple - take turns on the keyboard, switching whenever this symbol comes up...
Bump into the ball to get it moving!
In the game your ship will automatically rotate around the middle.
Take turns touching the ball and try passing to the other player!
While holding down 'SPACE' all ships are shrunk, making them faster.
Try playing through being shrunk, using 'SPACE'
Defend the ball back into the net
If the ball touches the striped outline, the enemy would score

Congratulations, that is all you need to know!

You are now ready for a competitive round.
